{"tid":1705595,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"恆地李家誠辭任16間物管公司董事，避潛在訴訟","createTime":"2019-11-11T02:00:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T02:31:07.000Z","uid":202464,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a0b914febfd0b17145d4b946eda5f0080f046fd7","tid":1705595,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T02:00:31.000Z","msg":"政府上月推蒙面法，恒地（012）聯席主席兼總經理李家誠立法當天（4日），停任至少16間有物業管理業務的公司董事，涉及多區爆發衝突之商場，<br />\n<br />\n包括馬鞍山新港城、屯門時代廣場、沙田中心等。千金之子坐不垂堂，有律師認為，停任董事可避免一切潛在訴訟。<br />\n<br />\n警察肆意進入商場抓捕示威者，管理公司經常處於兩難局面，未來亦有不少潛在刑事或民事索償訴訟事"},{"pid":"bdfaf16f8568e32fda4d2fbbfa31ab58c5304050","tid":1705595,"uid":202464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T02:02:05.000Z","msg":"有分析認為，恒地早於立法當日預料到衝突會急速升溫，結果李家誠率先辭任離開危險地，僅維持股東身份。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n該批物管公司未見其他家族成員補位，亦無股權變化。董事局成員只餘下「四叔」八妹馮李煥瓊為家族成員，其餘為恒地外姓老臣子李鏡禹、薛伯榮、郭炳濠及孫國林等。"},{"pid":"038ce86bfdc355ddce48ccea83e9cbc0ddafc63b","tid":1705595,"uid":162910,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T02:05:39.000Z","msg":"真係先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e12748c914c8021d085bb1067d19ce9263f7eb5d","tid":1705595,"uid":60120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"038ce86bfdc355ddce48ccea83e9cbc0ddafc63b","tid":1705595,"uid":162910,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T02:05:39.000Z","msg":"真係先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T02:06:49.000Z","msg":"呢個係李家誠<br />\n唔撚係李嘉誠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmo